This session is being continued from a previous conversation that ran out of context. The summary below covers the earlier portion of the conversation.

Summary:
1. Primary Request and Intent:
   The user wanted to explore and implement P1 upgrade items for the SmartOA approval management system, working through each item step-by-step with git commits after each step. The work proceeded through: (1) JPA → MyBatis-Plus migration, (2) configurable approval engine with dynamic nodes, (3) 4 approval actions (withdraw + transfer), (4) Excel export + ECharts stats APIs, (5) frontend P1 upgrade, and (6) generating 7 project documentation files (PRD, API design, DB design, test, architecture, deployment, requirements spec). The user consistently said "一个一个来吧" (one at a time) and requested commits after each completed step. The user also noted that 00-选题标定.md is not needed since 46-简易 OA 审批流管理系统.md already serves that purpose.

2. Key Technical Concepts:
   - Spring Boot 4.0.6, JDK 21
   - MyBatis-Plus 3.5.9 (BaseMapper, LambdaQueryWrapper, IdType.AUTO, @TableName, @TableField, @TableId, @MapperScan)
   - JPA → MyBatis-Plus migration (Optional removal, getReferenceById → selectById, save → insert/updateById, Spring Data JPA method queries → LambdaQueryWrapper)
   - Configurable approval engine: approval_node table with sort_order for arbitrary N-level flow, approverType enum (DIRECT_LEADER/DEPARTMENT_HEAD/SPECIFIC_USER)
   - 6-table MySQL 8 schema: sys_user, approval_template, approval_node, template_field, leave_request, approval_record
   - JWT authentication with JJWT 0.12.6
   - Vue 3 + Vite + Element Plus + Pinia + ECharts frontend
   - Apache POI 5.3 for Excel export
   - provide/inject pattern for user name lookup across components
   - Frontend name mapping: backend returns IDs only, frontend uses userStore + inject('getUserName')

3. Files and Code Sections:

   **pom.xml** (modified twice - Steps 1 & 4):
   - Replaced spring-boot-starter-data-jpa with mybatis-plus-spring-boot3-starter:3.5.9
   - Removed h2 dependency
   - Added Apache POI 5.3.0
   - Added echarts to frontend package.json

   **application.properties** (Step 1):
   - Removed all JPA/Hibernate configuration
   - Added mybatis-plus.configuration.log-impl + map-underscore-to-camel-case

   **SmartoaApplication.java** (Step 1):
   ```java
   @SpringBootApplication
   @MapperScan("com.smartoa.mapper")
   public class SmartoaApplication {
   ```

   **Entity layer - all 6 entities rewritten:**

   User.java:
   ```java
   @Data @NoArgsConstructor @AllArgsConstructor
   @TableName("sys_user")
   public class User {
       @TableId(type = IdType.AUTO) private Long id;
       @TableField("username") private String username;
       @JsonIgnore @TableField("password") private String password;
       @TableField("real_name") private String realName;
       @TableField("role") private String role;
       @TableField("department") private String department;
       @TableField("direct_leader_id") private Long directLeaderId;
       @TableField("department_head_id") private Long departmentHeadId;
   }
   ```

   LeaveRequest.java (key fields after Step 2):
   ```java
   @TableName("leave_request")
   public class LeaveRequest {
       @TableId(type = IdType.AUTO) private Long id;
       @TableField("applicant_id") private Long applicantId;
       @TableField("template_id") private Long templateId; // NEW
       @TableField("leave_type") private String leaveType;
       // ... startDate, endDate, reason, status
       @TableField("approval_step") private Integer approvalStep;
       @TableField("current_node_id") private Long currentNodeId; // NEW
       @TableField("current_approver_id") private Long currentApproverId;
       @TableField("create_time") private LocalDateTime createTime;
       @TableField("update_time") private LocalDateTime updateTime;
   }
   ```

   ApprovalNode.java (NEW - Step 2):
   ```java
   @TableName("approval_node")
   public class ApprovalNode {
       @TableId(type = IdType.AUTO) private Long id;
       @TableField("template_id") private Long templateId;
       @TableField("node_name") private String nodeName;
       @TableField("sort_order") private Integer sortOrder;
       @TableField("approver_type") private String approverType; // DIRECT_LEADER|DEPARTMENT_HEAD|SPECIFIC_USER
       @TableField("approver_id") private Long approverId;
